---
title: Za’atar-Crusted Halloumi & Mixed Grains 3 easy steps to a delicious dinner
description: For this 15-minute vegetarian dish, you’ll coat grilling cheese (aka halloumi) in a za’atar spice blend and sear until golden. Serve it over a zucchini-studded grain blend seasoned with Vidalia onion and romesco sauce (a savory tomato-pepper-almond blend), then finish with a drizzle of yogurt for a wholesome, colorful, delicious meal—fast!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67734975d8e11bf886853da9-17950b0c.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/67734975d8e11bf886853da9-en-US.pdf
